- `bd-7oo` is only closed if the remaining child graph and documentation justify that claim.","notes":"This bead is the explicit anti-handwave mechanism. It now covers the full verification ladder, including shell e2e evidence and diagnostic artifacts, so the project does not silently drift from almost there to claimed complete.","status":"closed","priority":0,"issue_type":"task","estimated_minutes":180,"created_at":"2026-03-07T23:41:54.522351372Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-03-12T12:09:21.644902310Z","closed_at":"2026-03-12T12:09:21.641588918Z","close_reason":"Final parity verification sweep complete. 1,293 tests (1,291 passing, 2 pre-existing flaky). All rch validation passes. Docs verified accurate. Only residual gap is low-priority workspace auto-discovery convenience. bvr confirmed as functional replacement for legacy bv.","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"labels":["e2e","legacy-port","parity","verification"],"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"bd-7oo.6","depends_on_id":"bd-7oo","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-03-07T23:41:54.522351372Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-7oo.6","depends_on_id":"bd-7oo.1.5","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-03-07T23:41:57.351361904Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-7oo.6","depends_on_id":"bd-7oo.1.6","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-03-07T23:54:04.144755070Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-7oo.6","depends_on_id":"bd-7oo.2.4","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-03-07T23:41:57.443675191Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-7oo.6","depends_on_id":"bd-7oo.2.5","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-03-07T23:54:06.286013876Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-7oo.6","depends_on_id":"bd-7oo.3.3","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-03-07T23:41:57.537565802Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_